a. single target charisma buff<br>
Increase Charisma (40)<br>
b. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds, Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Allure-<br>
a. research only<br>
see Research for components needed<br>
b. single target charm<br>
c. max duration 8 minutes<br>
<br>
Berserker Spirit-<br>
a. single target buff<br>
Increase Strength (40)<br>
Decrease Agility (20) <br>
Absorb Damage (200) <br>
b. This spell does not stack well with other strength spells however, and is best used on caster classes as a cheap form of Rune.<br>
c. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds, Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Blanket of Forgetfulness-<br>
a. area effect hate reduction<br>
b. The primary advantage in this spell over others is that it has no check on magical resistances. As such the spell will always succeed in reducing the amount of taunt on a monsters hate list.<br>
c. this is a research spell (see Research for components) but can also be purchased from Caleah Herblender at The Herb Jar in South Qeynos.<br>
<br>
Dazzle-<br>
a. single target mez<br>
Mesmerise <br>
Reduce Hate<br>
b. A dazzled target has a chance of having its Hate List wiped<br>
c. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds, Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Enchant Admantite-<br>
a. Create a Bar of Enchanted Adamantite<br>
b. requires a Large Block of Adamantium<br>
c. can be purchased in Neriak Library<br>
<br>
Enchant Brellium-<br>
a. create a bar of enchanted Brellium<br>
b. requires a Large Brick of Brellium<br>
c. can be purchased in Ak`Anon Casters Guild<br>
<br>
Enchant Mithril-<br>
a. create a bar of enchanted Mithril<br>
b. requires a Large Brick of Mithril<br>
c. can be purchased in Felwithe Casters Guild<br>
<br>
Enchant Steel-<br>
a. creates a bar of enchanted Steel<br>
b. requires a Large Brick of High Quality Ore<br>
c. can be purchased in Freeport and Qeynos Casters Guilds <br>
<br>
Gasping Embrace-<br>
a. single target DoT<br>
Direct Damage (50)<br>
Decrease Strength (29 - 30)<br>
Decrease Agility (29 - 30)<br>
Damage over Time (660 over 2 min) <br>
b. does not stack with some Necro DoT's<br>
c. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qenos Casters Guilds, Erudin Palace Ench Guild and from Cleah Herblender at The Herb Jar in S. Qeynos<br>
<br>
Group Resist Magic-<br>
a. group buff<br>
Increase Magical Resistance (54 - 55)<br>
b. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds, Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Kintaz's Animation-<br>
a. summon pet<br>
b. This animation can dual wield if given a one handed weapon<br>
c. can be purchased in Highhold Keep<br>
<br>
Paralyzing Earth-<br>
a. research only spell (see Research for components)<br>
b. root<br>
<br>
Purify Mana-<br>
a. Summons a vial of purified mana for use in trade skills.<br>
b. requires a Ruby and a Poison Vial<br>
c. can be purchased from the Brownie Camp in Lesser Fay<br>
<br>
Reoccurring Amnesia-<br>
a. single target hate list reduction<br>
b. this is a research spell (see Research for components) and can also be purchased from Ghul Rusten at the docks in South Qeynos<br>
<br>
Shadow-<br>
a. single target buff<br>
AC Buff (Max: 20)<br>
b. This spell does not stack with the Cleric or Shaman AC spells<br>
c. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds, Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Swift Like The Wind-<br>
a. single target haste<br>
increases the targets attack rate by 60%<br>
b. It is primarily effective on players over Level 50<br>
c. It will stack with haste items, but not with any other haste spell or song.<br>
